    "The regulatory requirement to adhere to ethical standards, as mandated by the Act, could further reinforce the perception of ethics and regulations being an obstacle, highlighting the tension between rapid technological advancement and the need for responsible innovation.",
    "In addition, quote C.3 conveys a sentiment shared by some experts that although ethical considerations are undeniably important, they are sometimes viewed as hindrances to meaningful AI advancement, further highlighting the complex dynamics between ethical considerations and the pursuit of technological progress in AI.",
